
1. struct usb_device : Each usb client is enumerated as an instance of this
                       structure
2. struct usb_config : Each conifguration descriptor is enumerated as an
                       instance of this type.
3. struct usb_host_interface : Each interface descriptor is enumerated into an
                               instance of this type.

4. struct usb_interface : This is usb driver subsystem specific data structure used to represent a 
                          specific usb functionality( A usb function might comprise of multiple 
                          usb_host_interfaces called alternate settings)

5. struct usb_host_endpoint : Each endpoint descriptor is enumerated into an
                              instance of this type
